Package: xtop
Version: 0.46.0-1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6
Recommends: postgresql, journalctl
Installed-Size: 38000
Maintainer: Farhan Tahir <farhan.003@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/ftahirops/xtop
Description: Incident-first root-cause analysis console for Linux
 v0.46.0 ships two binaries: xtop (full TUI + hub + agent) and xtop-agent
 (standalone fleet agent, 14MB, no TUI). The dedicated agent runs in
 lean mode only, has a smaller import surface (no Bubbletea / lipgloss /
 app deep modules), and is the recommended way to monitor production
 hosts. Also ships v0.45.0 module config: ~/.xtop/modules.json with
 profile presets (minimal/standard/sre/investigation) plus per-collector
 toggles via the new `xtop modules` subcommand.
